{"tid":1324301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果721係對政府重力一擊就要去金鐘/中環/西環！！！","createTime":"2019-07-16T13:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:50:22.000Z","uid":224095,"like":24,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"53958696d4a015094b38cf27f4b3d3e9a1b703fa","tid":1324301,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"金鐘警犬玩就玩到熟哂，但如果去非金鐘/中環/西環呢啲地方根本同之前光復行動冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n針對唔到政權/香港經濟命脈，只會影響到民生，到時手足想做野又一大班和理非走出黎話留力又剩。<br />\n<br />\n巷戰銅鑼灣個格局同旺角差唔多，而家唔係起革命打差佬打巷戰冇意思，甚至會分散示威者，警察亦容易包圍剿滅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣係令自己處於被動角色等警察出擊。如果警察唔理，好似以往9/6，16/6咁克制，警察唔出擊的話示威者又係on99一日。<br />\n<br />\n而前幾次搞到咁大係因為警察主動撩事鬥非。<br />\n<br />\n但今次警察明知人數將會係七月以黎最大規模，有機會變陣。<br />\n<br />\n星期日今次係自1/7後香港人召集，向政府重申五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n去銅鑼灣輸出革命做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0410ea06feb31e5e260dd970b71dd0e665448d33","tid":1324301,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:50:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"dfcb8de419d0d136816cf1c26538e28925791daf","tid":1324301,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53a046faf66d47be07b7323df42fb2d7a6fa73c6","tid":1324301,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"屌老母，第二個post都比我50連到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9d84396230cbbf142cb6fd4d69e7314119be8f","tid":1324301,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"421d55ed0d9778def073fc49ff7601cee766ea80","tid":1324301,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf335dfc1e7e1684a04bb116f1b9f122a6a6ab9","tid":1324301,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:05:10.00